trans-unit.target: Gir valgfrie innstillinger for en <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"></xref> class by copying the values of an existing <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"> </xref> klassen ved å kopiere verdiene i en eksisterende <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContextSettings"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether a XAML schema and its context use fully qualified assembly names in the values that are returned by the lookup API.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om et XAML-skjema og konteksten bruke fullstendige samlingsnavn i verdiene som returneres av oppslaget API.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property influences the strings that are returned by <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.GetAllXamlNamespaces%2A> in the constructed schema context.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen påvirker strenger som returneres av <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.GetAllXamlNamespaces%2A>i konteksten konstruert XML-skjema.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.GetAllXamlNamespaces%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.FullyQualifyAssemblyNamesInClrNamespaces%2A> is `true`, the assembly part of the string reports the equivalent of <xref:System.Reflection.Assembly.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if a XAML schema and its context use fully qualified assembly names in the values that are returned by the lookup APIs; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis et XAML-skjema og konteksten bruker fullstendige samlingsnavn i verdiene som returneres av oppslaget APIer; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether a XAML schema context allows for markup extensions that have two constructors with the same arity (number of input parameters).
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om en XAML skjemaet kontekst tillater markup utvidelser som har to konstruktører med samme aritet (antall Inndataparametere).

trans-unit.source: From a <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext>, you cannot read the settings directly.
trans-unit.target: Fra en <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext>, du kan ikke lese innstillingene for direkte.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext>

trans-unit.source: Instead, you receive values from specific read-only properties, such as <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.SupportMarkupExtensionsWithDuplicateArity%2A>, which report the settings-based values.
trans-unit.target: I stedet du mottar verdier fra bestemte skrivebeskyttede egenskaper, for eksempel <xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.SupportMarkupExtensionsWithDuplicateArity%2A>, hvilken rapport basert på innstillinger-verdier.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlSchemaContext.SupportMarkupExtensionsWithDuplicateArity%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the schema context allows for markup extensions that have duplicate arity; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis skjemaet konteksten tillater markup utvidelser som har identiske aritet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
